I mean,
who are these people?

48:55.980 --> 48:58.187
Maybe you just answered
your own question.

48:58.500 --> 49:00.787
Look at this.
Seventh Street.

49:00.940 --> 49:02.271
Is that your building?

49:02.420 --> 49:03.910
Yeah, but why
is it all red?

49:03.980 --> 49:05.220
You're being targeted
for something,

49:05.300 --> 49:06.426
along with all
these other buildings.

49:06.500 --> 49:08.309
Here, here.
All over the city.

49:08.380 --> 49:09.620
All around
the projects.

49:10.220 --> 49:11.551
Maybe you
were right, Cali.

49:11.700 --> 49:14.101
Look, I'm telling you, this
is the New Founding Fathers.

49:14.180 --> 49:15.341
- The government...
- The truck is fucked.

49:15.420 --> 49:18.469
No good? No, the engine's
all blown out or something.

49:20.060 --> 49:21.221
Hey, look at this.

49:22.940 --> 49:24.430
That's Carmelo's mark, Mom.

49:26.580 --> 49:28.070
I told Papa
he was the real deal.

49:28.140 --> 49:29.585
His group took
these fuckers out.

49:29.660 --> 49:30.980
Everybody got a weapon?

49:33.500 --> 49:36.583
Hey, grab this. Take the weapon.
Go. Go!

49:37.380 --> 49:38.791
Go! Oh, shit, there's
another one.

49:38.940 --> 49:40.305
Looks like an army.
Come on.

49:40.460 --> 49:42.303
Get down, let's go.

50:34.260 --> 50:35.421
Take this.

50:38.700 --> 50:39.747
Shh.

51:33.180 --> 51:34.784
Come on.

52:01.340 --> 52:02.501
Hey-

52:02.580 --> 52:05.311
Why did you stop
at our building?

52:05.380 --> 52:07.348
Why did you help us?

52:08.980 --> 52:11.426
Didn't we establish
a no-talking rule?

52:12.220 --> 52:14.871
People are getting
killed all over the city.

52:14.940 --> 52:16.908
Why did you stop for us?

52:19.100 --> 52:22.900
I saw you. You were putting
up a hell of a fight.

52:24.060 --> 52:26.028
You reminded me
of someone.

52:26.980 --> 52:28.141
Who?

52:31.980 --> 52:36.588
Look, Purging, no matter
what the reason, is wrong.

52:37.060 --> 52:38.949
Killing doesn't
help anything.

52:39.020 --> 52:40.067
It doesn't heal someone.

52:40.220 --> 52:42.461
Enough. Enough.

52:44.500 --> 52:46.821
Go back with
your mommy.

52:47.900 --> 52:49.311
Go.

53:08.340 --> 53:10.502
There's no air in here.

53:18.580 --> 53:20.582
Come over here.
Put this on.

53:20.740 --> 53:22.185
I don't need that.
Put it on, I said.

53:22.260 --> 53:24.069
I said I don't need it.
Put it on.

53:28.460 --> 53:30.383
Put your arm
through here.

53:34.100 --> 53:36.228
Now, hopefully,
you won't need it.

53:37.740 --> 53:39.344
Let's move.

53:47.700 --> 53:49.065
- What was that?
- Shh.

53:58.260 --> 53:59.750
There's no threat.

53:59.940 --> 54:02.386
They're just trying to
make it through the night.

54:03.180 --> 54:04.864
Keep moving.

54:12.100 --> 54:13.750
Hey, are you okay?

54:13.900 --> 54:15.823
I just wanna
get out of here.

54:33.900 --> 54:35.106
Oh, shit!

54:36.380 --> 54:37.461
Move!

54:37.780 --> 54:39.145
Go! Come on!

54:46.980 --> 54:48.345
Run! Move!

55:00.740 --> 55:01.866
Move!

55:07.500 --> 55:09.662
Get up! Get up!
Come on!

55:09.820 --> 55:11.060
Get up, get up, get up!

55:11.260 --> 55:13.501
Mom, we have
to go right now!

55:13.900 --> 55:15.743
Move it,
move it! Move!

55:21.340 --> 55:22.865
Go, go!

55:26.660 --> 55:27.741
Up. up, up!

55:36.060 --> 55:39.143
We're not gonna make it.
Fuck it.

55:43.100 --> 55:44.261
Shane!

55:45.220 --> 55:46.790
- What are you doing?
- Get down!

55:46.940 --> 55:48.942
What do we do?
Just shoot! Just shoot!

55:58.940 --> 56:00.146
Shane!

56:06.260 --> 56:08.308
Oh, my God. I'm fine,
I'm fine, I'm fine!

56:08.460 --> 56:10.462
Just keep shooting. Just
keep shooting. Go! Go!

56:28.300 --> 56:30.985
All right. You're okay.

56:31.860 --> 56:33.021
Stay here.
Give me this.

56:33.180 --> 56:36.707
I'm so sorry. I'm so
sorry, I'm so sorry.

56:37.460 --> 56:39.303
I was just so scared.

56:41.580 --> 56:42.866
You're bleeding.

56:42.940 --> 56:44.340
I cut it on the platform.
It's fine.

56:44.380 --> 56:45.506
We'll help you.
Just tell us...

56:45.580 --> 56:46.627
I said, it's fine!

56:48.660 --> 56:49.786
Get up. Get up.

56:54.460 --> 56:56.269
What's taking
them so long?

57:07.820 --> 57:10.630
Help! He's been shot!
I have no idea how bad.

57:13.500 --> 57:15.309
Open up.
We're gonna be fine, okay?

57:15.460 --> 57:18.703
Call your friend. Tell her we're close.
We're gonna get him up.

57:18.860 --> 57:21.147
Okay. Look at me.
Look at me, Shane. Yeah?

57:21.300 --> 57:23.541
One, two, three.
Get him up.

57:23.620 --> 57:25.031
Let's go!

57:32.540 --> 57:34.827
<i>There are
four hours and 30 minutes</i>

57:34.900 --> 57:37.301
<i>remaining in
this year's Purge.</i>

57:37.460 --> 57:40.942
Go! Just don't worry! Go!
Come on, come on!

57:45.300 --> 57:46.506
Keep moving!

57:46.660 --> 57:49.664
Go! Don't slow down!
Keep moving!

57:50.060 --> 57:51.107
It's right up ahead.

57:51.180 --> 57:52.670
Come on!

57:52.820 --> 57:54.822
Cali! Slow down!

58:04.020 --> 58:05.909
Hey, look,
that's her building!

58:05.980 --> 58:07.823
She said to meet
around the back.

58:18.500 --> 58:20.309
<i>We have a
target match on the civilians</i>

58:20.380 --> 58:23.111
<i>who attacked Truck 2.</i>

58:31.420 --> 58:34.026
She said,
"Meet us around the back."

58:36.300 --> 58:37.631
Tanya! Let us in!

58:38.180 --> 58:39.864
It's Eva and Cali!

58:43.300 --> 58:45.348
Holy shit!
You guys look like hell.

58:45.500 --> 58:47.582
Come on, come on, hurry up.
Get in here. Hurry up!

58:47.740 --> 58:49.902
Thank you. I don't like
being out here. Come on.

58:55.460 --> 58:56.666
All right.

58:58.580 --> 59:00.230
Bullet went right through.

59:03.420 --> 59:05.184
I can't believe you guys
went through all that stuff.

59:05.340 --> 59:06.990
It's just insane!

59:08.180 --> 59:10.626
Get him to the hospital first
thing after this is over.

59:10.700 --> 59:12.623
Yeah.
You'll be okay.

59:12.700 --> 59:14.623
It's gonna hurt like a son of a
bitch, but you're gonna be okay.

59:14.700 --> 59:17.021
Thanks.
I can't thank you enough.

59:17.180 --> 59:19.023
That's what you get
for being a hero.

59:28.220 --> 59:30.029
I need the car.
I know.

59:30.180 --> 59:31.545
Come on, everybody.
Eat, drink!

59:31.620 --> 59:33.349
Yes,
I recommend drinking.

59:33.420 --> 59:35.180
It's the best way to get
through the evening.

59:35.460 --> 59:36.621
And the food
is delicious.

59:36.700 --> 59:37.820
My mother's
a wonderful cook.

59:37.980 --> 59:39.584
My sister's
a testament to that.

59:39.780 --> 59:41.384
What the hell
does that mean?

59:41.460 --> 59:43.462
That she's
a good cook!

59:43.540 --> 59:44.985
You know, you didn't
have to go this far.

59:45.060 --> 59:46.824
Just having us here
was really enough.

59:46.900 --> 59:48.902
You guys have had
a terrible night.

59:49.060 --> 59:50.346
Get some food
in your system,

59:50.420 --> 59:52.024
and we'll get through
this together.

59:52.180 --> 59:53.306
Excuse me.

59:54.740 --> 59:56.105
Cali?

59:56.180 --> 59:58.911
I can't believe
nobody's drinking with me.

59:58.980 --> 01:00:00.186
What about you, tough guy?

01:00:00.300 --> 01:00:01.347
Want a drink?

01:00:01.540 --> 01:00:02.701
No, thanks.

01:00:03.380 --> 01:00:05.269
Okay-

01:00:05.340 --> 01:00:06.830
You're really going
back out there?

01:00:09.500 --> 01:00:11.821
Mmm!

01:00:12.340 --> 01:00:14.700
Relax! It's my father and my
brother-in-law. He's the super.

01:00:14.780 --> 01:00:17.306
They were just checking the building.
It's all good.

01:00:18.660 --> 01:00:21.903
Everyone, please don't mind
my husband's clothes.

01:00:22.340 --> 01:00:23.580
He's not Purging.

01:00:23.660 --> 01:00:25.788
He just thought
it was a crazy idea

01:00:25.860 --> 01:00:28.147
to go out and see
what's happening tonight.

01:00:28.220 --> 01:00:29.460
Yeah, I chickened out.

01:00:29.660 --> 01:00:31.788
No way
I was going out there.

01:00:31.860 --> 01:00:33.942
I don't know what the hell I was thinking.

01:00:34.100 --> 01:00:36.501
Thank God he came to his senses.
I mean, look at him.

01:00:36.660 --> 01:00:39.550
He would've been the laughingstock
of the neighborhood.

01:00:40.900 --> 01:00:43.062
That's not very nice,
Lorraine.

01:00:43.260 --> 01:00:45.911
I'm sorry. I didn't mean
for it to be mean.

01:00:46.060 --> 01:00:47.903
It's not mean,
it's just true.

01:00:49.260 --> 01:00:50.386
How's everything, Daddy?

01:00:50.460 --> 01:00:51.541
It's all good, baby.

01:00:51.700 --> 01:00:53.828
The building's
locked down and good.

01:00:54.020 --> 01:00:55.146
It's quiet.

01:00:55.300 --> 01:00:58.065
I see you had a rough
go of it, my friend.

01:00:58.140 --> 01:00:59.505
- Oh, yeah.
- Relax.

01:00:59.660 --> 01:01:01.981
Make yourself at home.
You're safe here.

01:01:02.060 --> 01:01:04.108
We are anti-Purge
in this household.

01:01:04.180 --> 01:01:06.342
Speak for yourself, Daddy.

01:01:06.940 --> 01:01:08.271
What does that mean?

01:01:08.420 --> 01:01:09.820
I could think of
a couple situations

01:01:09.860 --> 01:01:11.703
where Purging
could be the answer.

01:01:12.900 --> 01:01:14.743
- Like when?
- I'm not telling.

01:01:14.900 --> 01:01:17.380
I'm just saying,
don't piss me off, bitch.

01:01:19.460 --> 01:01:21.542
- Uh, please excuse my daughter.
- No, it's fine.

01:01:21.660 --> 01:01:24.425
And, please, if there's anything
else you need, just ask.

01:01:24.580 --> 01:01:26.184
I could use a clean shirt.

01:01:26.300 --> 01:01:28.462
Down the hall,
second door on the left.

01:01:28.620 --> 01:01:31.271
Top drawer of the bureau.
What's mine is yours.

01:01:37.260 --> 01:01:38.421
Okay. Excuse me, too.

01:01:38.540 --> 01:01:40.030
I'm gonna go to
the little girl's room

01:01:40.100 --> 01:01:41.780
'cause this wine is
going right through me.

01:01:41.900 --> 01:01:44.551
Come on, everyone,
please eat and drink.

01:01:44.620 --> 01:01:46.543
Come on. Honey?

01:02:20.380 --> 01:02:23.702
<i>This is News 10 reporting on a
lively Purge Night across the country.</i>

01:02:24.260 --> 01:02:26.308
<i>We have riots in
East Los Angeles,</i>

01:02:26.380 --> 01:02:28.826
<i>as well as record
participation in Pittsburgh.</i>

01:02:29.300 --> 01:02:30.745
He wasn't lying.

01:02:31.220 --> 01:02:32.267
This shit hurts.

01:02:32.340 --> 01:02:33.910
Aw, I'm sorry.

01:02:40.140 --> 01:02:42.142
You scared
the shit out of me.

01:02:43.580 --> 01:02:45.469
I thought
I was losing you.

01:02:52.980 --> 01:02:55.984
But I still think we
should tell your sister.

01:03:04.140 --> 01:03:05.346
You're an asshole.

01:03:05.420 --> 01:03:07.104
I'm sorry.
That's not funny.

01:03:07.180 --> 01:03:09.262
I'm sorry.
No, l got shot.

01:03:09.460 --> 01:03:11.940
Oh, are you gonna use this excuse
for the rest of our lives?

01:03:12.020 --> 01:03:13.226
Well, at least
the rest of the night.

01:03:13.300 --> 01:03:14.870
Okay.

01:03:14.940 --> 01:03:17.784
All right, people, let's change
the atmosphere up in here.

01:03:17.860 --> 01:03:21.069
No more Purge news.
No more nothing depressing.

01:03:21.220 --> 01:03:25.020
Let's put on some music, and let's
just liven it up a little bit, right?

01:03:25.100 --> 01:03:26.780
Come
on, you want to dance?

01:03:27.340 --> 01:03:28.671
Why not?

01:03:28.820 --> 01:03:30.663
Liven up the party,
come on.

01:03:31.180 --> 01:03:34.184
Let's dance.
Let's dance!

01:03:34.380 --> 01:03:36.189
Okay, I gotta go.
I need the car.

01:03:37.180 --> 01:03:38.944
I know.
You trust these people?

01:03:39.140 --> 01:03:41.268
Because your friend
likes to drink,

01:03:41.340 --> 01:03:42.910
and she's taking
pills back there.

01:03:43.100 --> 01:03:45.546
Yeah, she's pretty wild.

01:03:45.700 --> 01:03:48.271
But we'll be okay.
She's a good friend.

01:03:48.420 --> 01:03:50.582
What? You don't
wanna do it? What?

01:03:50.660 --> 01:03:52.344
Lorraine, do you care
if we dance?

01:03:52.500 --> 01:03:54.229
She doesn't even care. She's
not even paying attention.

01:03:54.300 --> 01:03:55.426
Now he's...
Look at him.

01:03:55.500 --> 01:03:57.025
He's asleep. He is.

01:03:58.340 --> 01:04:00.308
I don't know
how to thank you.

01:04:00.980 --> 01:04:04.587
Okay, if you can just tell her
I need the car right now,

01:04:04.740 --> 01:04:06.629
that would be
really great.

01:04:06.780 --> 01:04:08.987
I know what
you're doing tonight.

01:04:10.340 --> 01:04:13.184
You're going out there to
kill someone who wronged you.

01:04:13.380 --> 01:04:14.666
You believe in this night,
don't you?

01:04:14.820 --> 01:04:16.820
I think you should just
take care of your daughter.

01:04:16.980 --> 01:04:19.984
She's special,
and you're very lucky.

01:04:20.300 --> 01:04:22.507
And I need the car.

01:04:25.860 --> 01:04:27.624
There is no car.

01:04:28.340 --> 01:04:29.865
What?

01:04:30.540 --> 01:04:32.224
I'm sorry,
they don't have a car.

01:04:32.860 --> 01:04:34.988
But we needed you.

01:04:35.900 --> 01:04:37.265
And I needed the car.

01:04:37.420 --> 01:04:39.866
I did what I had to.
I did it for my daughter.

01:04:40.020 --> 01:04:42.182
I was doing this
for my son.

01:04:42.580 --> 01:04:44.503
And I trusted you.

01:04:46.380 --> 01:04:49.668
You have no idea what you might
have taken away from me tonight.

01:04:55.900 --> 01:04:58.107
Hey-
Hey-

01:04:58.220 --> 01:04:59.984
Look, I know you're
angry with my mother,

01:05:00.100 --> 01:05:01.909
but I really think you
should just stay here.

01:05:02.100 --> 01:05:04.751
Just wait out
the night with us, okay?

01:05:07.260 --> 01:05:10.150
Look, I heard you say that
you're doing it for your son.

01:05:10.780 --> 01:05:12.020
Now, I don't know him,

01:05:12.100 --> 01:05:13.511
but I'm sure he would
not want you to do

01:05:13.580 --> 01:05:15.100
whatever it is
that you're going to do.

01:05:16.100 --> 01:05:18.023
Bye, Cali. Please, come
on, you're safe here.

01:05:18.180 --> 01:05:19.670
Get out of my way.
Please, just...

01:05:19.820 --> 01:05:20.901
I gotta go. Goodbye.

01:05:21.060 --> 01:05:22.300
Stay here. It's fine.
Get out of the way.

01:05:22.660 --> 01:05:23.661
Get back!

01:05:25.580 --> 01:05:26.911
No!

01:05:27.980 --> 01:05:29.027
Lorraine!

01:05:29.180 --> 01:05:30.340
What are you doing?

01:05:31.740 --> 01:05:33.822
Tanya! Tanya!

01:05:36.420 --> 01:05:37.467
Lorraine!

01:05:38.900 --> 01:05:41.141
What've you done? What
are you doing, Lorraine?

01:05:41.300 --> 01:05:42.904
Jesus Christ,
she's dead.

01:05:43.100 --> 01:05:45.501
You killed your sister!
She's your sister!

01:05:45.660 --> 01:05:46.866
Lorraine!
What are you doing?

01:05:47.060 --> 01:05:48.141
You know
what I'm doing.

01:05:49.100 --> 01:05:51.421
I read all your emails,
you cheating motherfuckers.

01:05:51.740 --> 01:05:53.230
You both deserve to die!

01:05:55.100 --> 01:05:57.068
Okay, Lorraine!
Lorraine, stop!

01:05:57.900 --> 01:05:59.789
No! Get back, get back.
Back up, back up!

01:05:59.940 --> 01:06:01.021
I'm sorry, okay?
I'm sorry.

01:06:01.180 --> 01:06:02.660
What the fuck are you doing?
Lorraine.

01:06:02.740 --> 01:06:05.027
If you shoot me,
you shoot this woman.

01:06:05.100 --> 01:06:06.261
Just let her go!

01:06:06.660 --> 01:06:07.991
You don't
wanna do that!

01:06:08.140 --> 01:06:10.142
Lorraine, I'm sorry.
I didn't mean anything.

01:06:10.300 --> 01:06:13.144
I didn't mean it. She hasn't
done anything to you.

01:06:13.300 --> 01:06:14.870
Okay? So, cut this out!

01:06:15.220 --> 01:06:19.384
Fuck you! This is my right,
granted to me by my government.

01:06:22.060 --> 01:06:23.505
Leave him alone!
He's mine!

01:06:27.540 --> 01:06:29.190
Door, now. Go.

01:06:31.380 --> 01:06:32.984
Door! Go!

01:06:33.780 --> 01:06:35.111
Door, door, door!

01:06:35.260 --> 01:06:36.386
Now!

01:06:38.300 --> 01:06:39.586
Move, move, move!

01:06:49.100 --> 01:06:50.545
Go, go!

01:06:56.900 --> 01:06:58.868
I can't believe
Tanya's dead.

01:06:59.180 --> 01:07:01.023
What do we do now?
Where do we go?

01:07:29.060 --> 01:07:30.391
Are you gonna
leave us now?

01:07:30.660 --> 01:07:31.821
What?

01:07:31.940 --> 01:07:33.351
Are you gonna
leave us now?

01:07:49.620 --> 01:07:51.110
You've gotta be
fucking kidding me.

01:07:51.220 --> 01:07:52.506
Shh!
How did they find us?

01:07:53.260 --> 01:07:54.341
Stay here.

01:07:54.500 --> 01:07:55.581
Don't move!

01:08:14.140 --> 01:08:16.029
Do you think
he's gonna come back?

01:08:16.180 --> 01:08:18.751
What do we do
if he doesn't?

01:08:20.899 --> 01:08:22.982
Come on, guys.
Let's go, okay?

01:08:23.140 --> 01:08:26.064
We don't have all night. I
want this building surrounded.

01:08:27.540 --> 01:08:28.621
He's here.

01:08:28.779 --> 01:08:32.421
I know it, and I want him.
Understood?

01:08:32.580 --> 01:08:33.627
He shot me.

01:08:34.100 --> 01:08:37.899
He shot half my team.
I want him dead.

01:08:44.380 --> 01:08:46.381
Come on,
come on, come on.

01:08:46.740 --> 01:08:49.265
And I want
the two women he saved.

01:08:49.340 --> 01:08:50.785
They're mine.

01:08:50.859 --> 01:08:52.828
I want them alive.

01:08:57.899 --> 01:08:59.788
Please come back.

01:09:02.819 --> 01:09:05.426
They found us. Move fast, now.
Come on.

01:09:09.340 --> 01:09:10.501
Move now.
We have 30 seconds.

01:09:10.660 --> 01:09:13.106
Over the fence, fast.
Now. Go!

01:09:13.700 --> 01:09:15.145
Next. Come on,
come on, come on.

01:09:22.620 --> 01:09:24.782
Look at me. You go, you get
over that fence, you run.

01:09:24.939 --> 01:09:26.100
You don't stop.
You run for your life.

01:09:26.260 --> 01:09:27.988
Do you understand? You
don't fucking wait for me.

